GwiGwi.com – Warner Bros sudah merilis Trailer anyar dari film Detective Pikachu secara online, dan hasilnya ialah promo ini terus menjanjikan suatu film yang paling menyenangkan. Trailer ini sudah tentu akan memanjakan semua penggemar franchise Pokemon sebab menampilkan tidak sedikit sekali “cameo” seperti Bulbasaur, Jigglypuff, Psyduck, Squirtle, Aipom, Charizard, Mr. Mime, Loudred, Snorlax,…

blog.title: △ にゅーホログラム △
blog.description:
△ New Hologram △

♪ model, artist, gamer, fairy, spoonie ♫

Hi, I'm New! 🎀 *:･ﾟ✧*:･ﾟ✧

Divine ultraterrestrial demon-possessed entity at your service

Welcome to my personal blog.

→ My goal is to create a platform for awareness, visibility, and guidance for topics like chronic illness, mental illness, disability, trauma, and suicide. I also do Let's Plays, J-Pop translations, beauty vlogs, and more!

My chronic illness story - an introduction and mission statement

☆ PATREON Find out how you can support my work.

☎ YouTube

Check out my channel for chronic illness vlogs, Let's Plays, and more

See my work at ✨New Hologram Official

☂chronic illness guidance sideblog

🌸Instagram

☮ Twitter

♫ My J-Pop translations

Want to support my content?

↑I now have a "tip jar!"↑

And a Patreon!

I live with fibromyalgia, narcolepsy, ulcerative colitis and other conditions that come along with them. I'm currently in recovery from living 20+ years with undiagnosed atlas subluxation complex and the resulting osteoarthritis (degenerative disc disease). Even with these challenges, I work as much as I can at multiple jobs (currently at 3, working on getting up to 4!) and my free time is used to work on content. Most of my paychecks go into caring for myself but I try to keep my schedule open for work. If I can't work enough, I can't afford my treatments or medications, and most of it isn't covered by insurance so it's out of pocket. If I can't take care of myself, I struggle at work, and I can't work on videos or resources either because my free time then needs to be devoted to recovery. It's kind of a vicious cycle but I strive to stick to a schedule that allows me to use my day off energy to creating content while still saving time for resting. ​ ​Your donations and patronage allow me to afford what I need to care for my body while still being able to follow my passions. Thank you so much for supporting my dreams.​
